# Edge Functions

This directory contains your edge functions. Each subdirectory represents a single function.

## Creating a Function

```bash
bb function create my-function
```

This creates:
- `src/functions/my-function/index.ts` - The function code
- `src/functions/my-function/config.ts` - Function configuration

## Available Commands

- `bb function create <name>` - Create a new edge function
- `bb function dev <name>` - Run function locally with hot reload
- `bb function build <name>` - Bundle function for deployment
- `bb function list` - List all functions
- `bb function deploy <name>` - Deploy to Cloudflare Workers or Vercel Edge
